attributes.title: VERY POORLY MADE😭
attributes.review: Upon downloading this app, I was extremely disappointed. As soon as I opened the app, I was greeted with cotton balls and sugar cane with the message “Tap to gain rights ” over them.  While setting up my account, a message popped up, saying, “you’re only 3/5ths of the way there!”that shocked me I tapped “okay” and tried to set up my username. It gave me an auto generated username which read “slave monkey👨🏾‍🌾”. I clicked “redo” and it generated the username “Thug Ni**er”. Since making my account I have received numerous emails from the app telling me to “comb my nappy hair” and to “Go back to Africa”. The app also ordered me 20 boxes of Food stamps and fried chicken and mailed it to my home. I happily took the chicken and threw away the food stamps. As black woman, I am highly dissatisfied with the quality of this app.
